From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: guix-geng-project <noreply@example.com>
Date: Wed, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix: use Slicer_MAIN_PROJECT_APPLICATION_NAME for Slicer 5.8 compatibility

Slicer_MAIN_PROJECT_APPLICATION_DISPLAY_NAME was added in a newer Slicer
version and is not defined in vtkSlicerConfigure.h for Slicer 5.8.1.
The comment on the include line already names the correct 5.8 define.
---
 Applications/SlicerCustomAppTemplateApp/Main.cxx | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Applications/SlicerCustomAppTemplateApp/Main.cxx b/Applications/SlicerCustomAppTemplateApp/Main.cxx
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/Applications/SlicerCustomAppTemplateApp/Main.cxx
+++ b/Applications/SlicerCustomAppTemplateApp/Main.cxx
@@ -50,7 +50,7 @@
   if (!window.isNull())
     {
-    QString windowTitle = QString("%1 %2").arg(Slicer_MAIN_PROJECT_APPLICATION_DISPLAY_NAME).arg(Slicer_MAIN_PROJECT_VERSION_FULL);
+    QString windowTitle = QString("%1 %2").arg(Slicer_MAIN_PROJECT_APPLICATION_NAME).arg(Slicer_MAIN_PROJECT_VERSION_FULL);
     window->setWindowTitle(windowTitle);
     }

